data.description: Absolutely Charming and spacious 3 Bedrooms, 2 bath ranch house located in the quiet and desirable community of Hillbrook Estates in Muscogee County.  Conveniently located with easy access to J.R. Allen Hwy/US80, Columbus Park Crossing, (Whittlesey shopping area), Old Town, Columbus Airport, the Landings shopping area, and Columbus State University.  Move in Ready Condition!   The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, glass cabinets, and expansive countertops.  The living room opens into dining room with picture frame opening between den and living room, kitchen and dining rooms.  Extra's include sunroom, deck and fenced back yard.  This house is great for entertaining.  Don't miss out, this won't last long!
